{"tid":424020,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"姊弟戀揮手區","createTime":"2017-10-04T11:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T19:31:53.000Z","uid":148533,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3d233cb4bf0c8009b82fa08227a81f09e19a04fb","tid":424020,"uid":148533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:03:49.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊左半年多啲 <br />\n計落我25歲 出左嚟做左兩年嘢 <br />\n佢先畢業<br />\n我同佢都有傾過下未來嘅事<br />\n佢自己又易自卑 怕養我唔起<br />\n但我次次都有話唔緊要 其實可以自己賺錢<br />\n再一齊儲錢咁<br />\n但好怕到時經歷左兩年現實差距又擴大<br />\n想知道有無人同我一樣會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我好想同到男朋友繼續落去 唔係想分手<br />\n求巴絲們比下意見 或者分享下自己經歷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"207c6c477bdfb4ee0d2fded8531120590a9530f0","tid":424020,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c75561dce3087e0663b52525739f736780f231a","tid":424020,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">基路難行，回頭是岸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"6d9242525a9350698e126efce8a9e0e46eb6e178","tid":424020,"uid":119379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  A0死毒撚 日撚日係到ff識到女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？</blockquote><br />\n個個post都見到同一黎段野，屌"},{"pid":"55656ef89d5ea7fadf419cac26aea58b524c0fd7","tid":424020,"uid":148533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T13:12